          "style_family": null,
          "text": "深闺独处整红妆，承欢膝下慰高堂。五色绒线彩球绣，二月二日选佳郎。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（丫鬟暗上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我，王宝钏。爹爹王允，官居当朝首相；母亲陈氏，生我姐妹三人：大姐金钏"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "许配苏龙，二姐银钏许配魏虎，只我尚未婚配。只因那年母亲染病，我在床前"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "侍奉汤药，直到三载，母亲病体痊愈。正宫娘娘见喜，赐我五色绒线，绣成彩"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "球，定于二月二日高搭彩楼，抛球招赘。但愿得配如意郎君，方为终身之幸。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今当正月，大雪初晴，园中梅花盛开，正好前去观赏。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丫鬟，引路花园。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "银光耀目雪初晴，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "新春天气也宜人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "无边玉宇净无尘。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "满树梅花吐芳芬。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "几处楼台如画境"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "叫丫鬟带路花园进"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三姑娘，您瞧今年的梅花开得多好哇。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "果然开得茂盛。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我去给您掐一枝去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我在亭中等你。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛平贵上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "腹中饥饿身寒冷，"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "头晕目眩难支持。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "霎时只觉站立不稳……"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛平贵倒地。丫鬟折梅送给王宝钏。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊丫鬟，闲坐在此，想个主意玩耍？"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我拿棋盘去，跟您下棋吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不好。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咱们打秋千玩儿吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "也不好。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要不然……咱们上花园外边看看雪景去好不好？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王宝钏愿意，迟疑。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "相爷可在府中？"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老爷上朝去了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此开了花园门。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（丫鬟开门。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哟，这是谁倒卧在雪地上啦？"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小姐，外面有个人倒卧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待我前去看来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀且住！看此人面目清秀，仪表非凡，因何落魄至此？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丫鬟，快将此人唤醒。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "花郎醒来，花郎醒来！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛平贵醒来惊起。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来是位大姐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这是相府的花园门口，你怎么倒卧在这儿了呢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是我行至此处，忽觉头晕目眩，径自倒卧在此。有劳大姐将我唤醒，当面谢过。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你别谢我；快谢谢我们小姐去吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢小姐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丫鬟，将这花郎带进花园，我要周济于他。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我们小姐要周济你哪，跟我进来吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这……噢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，那一花郎，你姓甚名谁，家住哪里，因何落到这般光景？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "难人薛平贵，乃长安人氏。自幼曾读诗书，略通武艺。只因父母双亡，一贫如"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "洗，意欲投军报效，也好有个出头之日，不想饥寒交迫，倒卧在此。唉！真真"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "愧煞人也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "难人祖居长安境，"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "自幼曾学武和文。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "流落他乡受苦情。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "因此立志去从军。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "父母下世家计紧"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "男儿报国当发奋"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "父母下世家计紧"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "男儿报国当发奋"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "听他言来自思忖，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "他分明是个有志的人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "不如与他订婚姻。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "彩楼之事对他论……"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "父母下世家计紧"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "男儿报国当发奋"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "父母下世家计紧"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "男儿报国当发奋"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "又恐丫鬟一旁听。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "父母下世家计紧"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "男儿报国当发奋"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那一花郎，你可曾用饭？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "抛球选婿事不稳"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这个……咳！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丫鬟，看他甚是可怜，你去取些银米前来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（丫鬟下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "方才听你之言，父母双亡，你可有……"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可有妻室否？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想我一贫如洗，怎能娶妻呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我有一言不好启齿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小姐有话但讲何妨？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳，我对你实说了吧：我家为我终身之事，二月二日在十字街前高搭彩楼，抛"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "球招赘。不知你……可愿去否？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "蒙小姐如此见爱，真乃出于望外。只是我乃落魄之人，小姐你是千金之体，如"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何使得？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我既以终身相托，你、你就不必迟疑了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "相府招赘，接彩之人必然是王孙公子，只恐平贵无份哪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不妨，到了那日，你早些前去，站在彩楼之前，我自有道理。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "必当紧记。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "二月二日事有准，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我的言语要记明。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "万事只怕有心人。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（丫鬟上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三姑娘，银米在此。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "付与花郎，叫他去吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "给你，你去吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢小姐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "辞别小姐出园门，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唤他转来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "花郎回来，小姐叫你哪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "小姐有话请说明。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "二月二日勿失信，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "莫做薄情无义人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "小姐不必细叮咛，"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "平贵岂是无义人。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛平贵下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "回房去吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "心中暗把天祝定，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "早与平贵配良姻。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（丫鬟、王宝钏同下。）"
        }
      ],
